study_design_info.intervention_model_description:
Fifty-two subjects will be enrolled and randomized to one of the four treatment (Cohorts 1 to 4) in a ratio of 4:3:3:3 as described below:
Treatment 1 (n=16) - ATV-PG 1000-400 mg + AQ 612 mg;
Treatment 2 (n=12) - ATV-PG 1000-400 mg + AQ unmatched placebo;
Treatment 3 (n=12) - ATV-PG unmatched placebo + AQ 612 mg;
Treatment 4 (n=12) - ATV-PG unmatched placebo + AQ unmatched placebo.
